## 4  Value-Only Parameter Streaming
LLM sends a JSON object field-by-field.  We want to stream **only the value slices** (not keys / braces).  The helper set:
* `FieldSpec` тАУ static description of which JSON key maps to which UI keys.
* `StreamSpec` тАУ trait implemented on your params struct returning a `&'static [FieldSpec]` slice.
* `map_param_chunk::<P>()` тАУ generic fn that extracts `(ui_key, slice)` for every visible field in an incoming chunk.

### Why value-only?
тАв front-end UX is cleaner  
тАв prevents accidental exposure of hidden keys  
тАв allows per-field visibility toggles.

