## 6  Adding a New Tool тАУ Checklist
1. Create a params struct (`serde::Deserialize`) and mark visible fields via `impl StreamSpec`.  
2. Implement `ToolExecutor` (and optionally `StreamingToolExecutor` if you need chunking).  
3. Add a `ToolStreamer` mapping тАУ usually 2-3 lines thanks to `map_param_chunk`.  
4. Write unit tests following the patterns in section 5.  
5. Add the tool to the agent registry so the LLM can call it (see `agents/src/tools/registry.rs`).  
6. Update `docs/openapi.yaml` if it's a REST-exposed tool.

