## 7  Troubleshooting
| Symptom | Likely Cause | Fix |
|---------|--------------|-----|
| `trait bound ... StreamingToolExecutor not satisfied` | Forgot to implement the trait for your tool | Add `impl StreamingToolExecutor for MyTool` or use helper macro. |
| UI receives braces / key names | Your params struct missing `StreamSpec` or wrong `json_key` | Check `stream_fields()` entries. |
| Duplicate `ParamsComplete` events | Ingest parser resets buffer incorrectly | Ensure you only push once after `serde_json::from_str` succeeds. |

